msgstr ""
"_此功能仍在積極開發中。請參考[相關議題](https://github.com/PyO3/pyo3/"
"issues/1632)。_"

#: src/async-await.md:5
msgid "`#[pyfunction]` and `#[pymethods]` attributes also support `async fn`."
msgstr "`#[pyfunction]` 與 `#[pymethods]` 屬性也支援 `async fn`。"

